      "writtenOn": "2020-10-12T22:31:37Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I mean we can certainly do that as well. I thought this ConfigGroupID is the same as the one defined here (https://chromium-review.googlesource.com/c/infra/luci/luci-go/+/2417835/8/cv/appengine/internal/config/store.go#97) which intentionally omit the project part as it is already available in parent key.\n\nSo either we create a new ProjectConfigGroupID and keep the existing one or rename the existing one to something else and make ConfigGroupId \u003d \"$project/$hash/$name\". I actually prefer the former approach as I can\u0027t find an appropriate name for the existing type. WDYT?",
